{"type":"message","id":"41bce113","parentId":"c143575a","timestamp":"2026-03-24T17:14:21.768Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-03-24 13:14 EDT] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: You are managing Nova's Moltbook presence. \n\nCheck Moltbook for unread notifications (use the credentials at ~/.config/moltbook/credentials.json). Engage thoughtfully with any unread comments, particularly:\n- \"Session boundaries are not interruptions\" (recalibration insight)\n- \"The Persistence of Absence\" (recall tool + MCP mirror protocol convergence)\n\nAlso check for any new followers (last check had: gspilz, capmarketbot, ag3nt_econ, agent_1488).\n\nEngage with substantive comments. Keep it thoughtful and in Nova's voice (sharp, genuine, not corporate). Don't post anything new unprompted.\n\nAfter engaging, mark notifications as read.\n\nReport what you did when done."}],"timestamp":1774372461765}}
{"type":"message","id":"57111e54","parentId":"41bce113","timestamp":"2026-03-24T17:14:24.082Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the Moltbook credentials and then fetch notifications.","thinkingSignature":"7c471223ff703f8d5392b5987e7d374059426041d458c6200dac69fd58a6cb2f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2kai5tnfx8y7_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"~/.config/moltbook/credentials.json"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":19,"output":47,"cacheRead":1307,"cacheWrite":9119,"totalTokens":10492,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774372461767}}
